-- Suffolk Regional Off-Track Betting Files for Bankruptcy
-- B y   D a w n   M c C a r t y
-- 2012-05-12T02:34:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-12/suffolk-regional-off-track-betting-files-for-bankruptcy-in-n-y-.html
Suffolk Regional Off-Track Betting
Corp. filed for court protection under Chapter 9 today in U.S.
Bankruptcy Court in  Central Islip , New York, saying it owed
creditors more than $10 million.  Chapter 9 bankruptcy allows municipalities to reorganize
rather than liquidate.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dawn McCarty in Wilmington at 
 dmccarty@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
